  <p>Smart Layout allows you to create variations of your experience that are tailored to the typical audiences visiting the page.</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li>The variations are automatically generated by <a href="https://www.adobe.com/sensei.html">Adobe Sensei</a> based on data and segments from <a href="https://www.adobe.com/analytics/adobe-analytics.html">Adobe Analytics</a>.</li> 
   <li>The variations are delivered using <a href="https://www.adobe.com/marketing/target.html">Adobe Target</a>.</li> 
   <li>You can review and make changes to the proposed variations before publishing.</li> 
  </ul> 
